World Bank Says Volatile Commodity Prices a Critical Challenge

-- B y   S h a m i m   A d a m
-- 
2011-09-24T21:36:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-24/world-bank-says-volatile-commodity-prices-a-critical-challenge.html
The World Bank Development
Committee said volatile commodity prices and pressures on food
security are “critical challenges.”  While developing countries have led global growth, the
economic crisis has hurt their ability to withstand further
shocks, the committee said in a statement today after meeting in
 Washington .  To contact the reporter on this story:
